OL,3,CPrudhoe Community High School to be
OL,4,Cclosed for months as building 'not
OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,FPrudhoe Community High School will be
OL,8,Fclosed for at least six to nine months
OL,9,Fafter structural engineers advised
OL,10,Fthat the building is not safe.
OL,12,FInvestigations have been taking place
OL,13,Fsince a floor crack was identified in
OL,14,Fthe upper floor on 10 February.
OL,16,FInitially the building was considered
OL,17,Fsafe to open, but it has been closed
OL,18,Fall this week.
