OL,3,CPrudhoe Community High School to be
OL,4,Cclosed for months as building 'not
OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,FIn a letter to parents on Friday (21
OL,8,FFebruary), the Cheviot Learning Trust
OL,9,Fhas confirmed that they have been
OL,10,Fadvised that a long-term closure is
OL,11,Fnecessary.
OL,13,FThis week, students have been taking
OL,14,Fpart in online learning, and the trust
OL,15,Fhas said they are exploring all
OL,16,Foptions to restore face-to-face
OL,17,Flearning as soon as possible.
