OL,5,Csafe'
OL,7,FThis could involve relocating onto
OL,8,Fanother site, partial relocation of
OL,9,Fcertain year groups or building of
OL,10,Ftemporary mobile classrooms.
OL,12,FOne possible explanation for the
OL,13,Fdamage which is being investigated, is
OL,14,Fthat high winds from storm Eowyn in
OL,15,FJanuary may have been a trigger event
OL,16,Ffor the initial building movement.
OL,18,FHowever this has not been confirmed
OL,19,Fand further investigations are
OL,20,Fcontinuing to identify the root cause
OL,21,Fof the problem.
