OL,7,FIn the letter to parents, the chief
OL,8,Fexecutive officer of the Cheviot
OL,9,FLearning Trust, Alice Witherow,
OL,10,Fexpressed her thanks to all the
OL,11,Fparents, staff and community members
OL,12,Ffor their support, describing it as a
OL,13,F"very challenging situation".
